## Makefile: factorial for Linux
CC=gcc
CFLAGS=-Og -Wall
SYMBOLS=_SYSTEM64_
## -D_SYSTEM64_
SRC=factorial.c main.c
OBJ=factorial64.o main64.o
TARGET=factorial64

factorial64.o: factorial.c
	$(CC) $(CFLAGS) -D$(SYMBOLS) $< -c -o $@

main64.o: main.c
	$(CC) $(CFLAGS) -D$(SYMBOLS) $< -c -o $@

all: factorial64.o main64.o
	$(CC) $(CFLAGS) -D$(SYMBOLS) $(OBJ) -o $(TARGET)
clean:
	rm -rf $(OBJ) $(TARGET)
